Validation is still blocked by the sandbox, not by a Rust test failure. `cargo fmt --all` passed, but `cargo test --locked -p calypso-cli state` now fails during compilation with `Invalid cross-device link (os error 18)` while rustc writes `.rmeta` files, even after moving `TMPDIR` and `CARGO_TARGET_DIR` into `/tmp`. Because validation did not pass, I did not commit, update the PR checklist, or update the stale local implementation plan yet.
